# AgentEasePro Web - Environment Variables
# Copy this file to .env and fill in your values

# API Server URL (required)
VITE_API_URL=http://localhost:3001

# ============================================
# Property Intelligence APIs (optional)
# ============================================

# Census Bureau API Key (free)
# Get yours at: https://api.census.gov/data/key_signup.html
# VITE_CENSUS_API_KEY=your_census_api_key_here

# Walk Score API Key (free tier: 5,000 requests/day)
# Get yours at: https://www.walkscore.com/professional/api-sign-up.php
# VITE_WALK_SCORE_API_KEY=your_walk_score_api_key_here

# ============================================
# Notes
# ============================================
# The Property Intelligence Panel works without API keys using:
# - Static OpenStreetMap tiles for map previews
# - County assessor public website links
# - Portal deep links (Zillow, Realtor, etc.)
#
# With API keys configured, you'll also get:
# - Census: Median income, population, housing data by ZIP
# - Walk Score: Walkability, transit, and bike scores
